channel.title: Archaios / 724 / Economy
channel.description:
[center]The Archaios Home website is: Archaios.tk, make sure you check it out. The Archaios Forum is: Archaios.foumotion.com, make sure you check it out.
Archaios is a new server that has just reached the end of its coding, Archaios has many features that some other servers may not have. Archaios a new fully coded 724 RSPS looking for new members ready to play a skilling/economy server.
Archaios is run by mainly two people Luke & Evan They are the two main Developers of this server, they take their job very seriously and are always trying to make Archaios better.
Archaios is a new server so yes we are on the lookout for staff, but this gives no one the right to beg for a spot on the Archaios staff team, matter of fact this would lower your chances of getting on the staff team.
Archaios has almost every skill working and is a very fun server, we will have many events and rare item give-aways to start off the server and see where it goes from there. We also have Fully Working Dicing
At the moment this is the Archaios Staff:
Developers:
Luke & Evan
Administrators:
None
Moderators:
Alpha
We hope to see you online soon.
~Archaios Staff
The Archaios Forum is: Archaios.forumotion.com, make sure you check it out. The Archaios Home website is: Archaios.tk, make sure you check it out.[/center]
